Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}{\a6}O Amuro-{\i1}san{\i0} é um moço muito gentil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}{\a6}Edogawa-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}{\a6}Não me pergunte.
